imdb.title: Callie-Anne Cooks Into the Wild
akas: Callie-Anne Cooks Into the Wild (South Africa)
plot: Callie-Anne Rodgers is a food-enthusiast, traveler and author. Together with her family, Callie manages a luxury safari camp in Mozambique, where she prepares all meals on a gas stove with no electricity.
